import React from 'react'
import "./Features.css"
import { Link, Outlet } from 'react-router-dom'
import Product from './Products/Product'
import Rose from './Products/Rose'
import Leli from './Products/Leli'
import Jar from './Products/Jar'


function Features() {
  return (
    <>
    <nav>
<Link to={<Rose/>}>Rose</Link>
<Link to={<Leli/>}>Leli</Link>
<Link to={<Jar/>}>Jar</Link>
    </nav>
<Product/>
<Outlet/>
    </>
  )
}

export default Features
